        "text": "<p>Applications will not be accepted unless ALL of the following requirements are met:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Applications should be submitted at least 40 days prior to the date of the event. Unless your event meets exemption requirements, no applications will be accepted if they are received less than five (5) days prior to the date of the event;</li>\n<li>A permit processing fee of $150.00 is required.</li>\n<li>The signature of the applicant must be included</li>\n<li>Details describing all marching groups, parade floats, elements, vehicles, signs, banners, props, etc., must be included;&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>",
